\f0\fs24 \cf0 Your assignment is to write a job description for a position related to audio script. Refer to the reading assignment and the DVD that comes with the textbook for information to get you started. The book primarily focuses on visual media for entertainment and for corporate video projects. There are a host of other types of jobs that aren\'92t covered in the reading, like for video games or websites. \ \ You should include in your paper, but please don\'92t limit your paper to, the following: \ \ * A list of skills needed to complete the job (keep in mind we\'92re dealing with new media, web, video, etc.).\ * Qualifications\ * Salary Range\ }
